ist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-with-island-010725-843-10-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-with-island-010725-843-11.jpg\" alt=\"The ceiling rises over the kitchen to a skylight, increasing light and volume. A large island anchors the space, while a horizontal window above the counter provides a framed view of the forest. Behind a paneled wall, a separate pantry kitchen adds functionality without disrupting the open layout.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-with-island-010725-843-11.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-with-island-010725-843-11-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-with-island-010725-843-11-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-with-island-010725-843-11-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-with-island-010725-843-11-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-with-island-010725-843-11-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eOn the lower level, a spacious lounge connects to a game room outfitted with a pool table and bar. These spaces encourage relaxed gathering and extend the home’s function beyond seasonal retreat.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1913\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-games-room-010725-844-12.jpg\" alt=\"On the lower level of this modern house, a spacious lounge connects to a game room outfitted with a pool table and bar. These spaces encourage relaxed gathering and extend the home’s function beyond seasonal retreat.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-games-room-010725-844-12.jpg 1913w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-games-room-010725-844-12-940x1258.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-games-room-010725-844-12-800x1071.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-games-room-010725-844-12-768x1028.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-games-room-010725-844-12-1148x1536.jpg 1148w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-games-room-010725-844-12-1530x2048.jpg 1530w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1913px) 100vw, 1913px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe primary suite includes a fireplace, floor-to-ceiling windows, and sweeping lake views. There’s also a walk-in closet finished with wood doors offering generous storage.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-010725-842-13.jpg\" alt=\"The primary suite includes a fireplace, floor-to-ceiling windows, and sweeping lake views. There\u0026#39;s also a walk-in closet finished with wood doors offering generous storage.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-010725-842-13.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-010725-842-13-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-010725-842-13-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-010725-842-13-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-010725-842-13-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAn ensuite bathroom features a stone-clad shower and a freestanding tub positioned to face the scenery.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-design-010725-841-17.jpg\" alt=\"An ensuite bathroom features a stone-clad shower and a freestanding tub positioned to face the scenery.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-design-010725-841-17.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-design-010725-841-17-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-design-010725-841-17-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-design-010725-841-17-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-design-010725-841-17-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-design-010725-841-17-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eA guest bedroom has a warm, natural aesthetic, with a wall of wide-plank wood paneling adding texture and warmth to the space.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-010725-842-15.jpg\" alt=\"A guest bedroom with a warm, natural aesthetic, with a wall of wide-plank wood paneling adding texture and warmth to the space.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-010725-842-15.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-010725-842-15-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-010725-842-15-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-010725-842-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-010725-842-15-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAnother bedrooms is designed specifically for children, complete with custom bunk beds and proximity to the shared family lounge.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-bunk-beds-010725-842-16.jpg\" alt=\"This modern bedroom is designed specifically for children, complete with custom bunk beds and proximity to the shared family lounge.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-bunk-beds-010725-842-16.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-bunk-beds-010725-842-16-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-bunk-beds-010725-842-16-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-bunk-beds-010725-842-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-bunk-beds-010725-842-16-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn another bathroom, there’s a serene and luxurious atmosphere. The space features a freestanding matte white bathtub, while the walls and floors are clad in large-format gray stone tiles that create a cohesive, monolithic look. A frameless glass partition separates the wet area, which includes a walk-in shower with a ceiling-mounted rainfall showerhead and a matte black hand shower set.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-design-010725-841-18.jpg\" alt=\"In this bathroom there\u0026#39;s a serene and luxurious atmosphere. The space features a freestanding matte white bathtub, while the walls and floors are clad in large-format gray stone tiles that create a cohesive, monolithic look. A frameless glass partition separates the wet area, which includes a walk-in shower with a ceiling-mounted rainfall showerhead and a matte black hand shower set.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-design-010725-841-18.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-design-010725-841-18-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-design-010725-841-18-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-design-010725-841-18-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-design-010725-841-18-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-design-010725-841-18-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eHere’s a look at the floor plan for the home, showing how it’s organized over two levels.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1290\" height=\"846\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-architecture-floor-plan-010725-841-19.jpg\" alt=\"Here\u0026#39;s a look at the floor plan for a modern home.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-architecture-floor-plan-010725-841-19.jpg 1290w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-architecture-floor-plan-010725-841-19-940x616.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-architecture-floor-plan-010725-841-19-800x525.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-architecture-floor-plan-010725-841-19-768x504.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1290px) 100vw, 1290px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1248\" height=\"772\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-architecture-floor-plan-010725-841-20.jpg\" alt=\"Here\u0026#39;s a look at the floor plan for a modern home.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-architecture-floor-plan-010725-841-20.jpg 1248w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-architecture-floor-plan-010725-841-20-940x581.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-architecture-floor-plan-010725-841-20-800x495.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-architecture-floor-plan-010725-841-20-768x475.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1248px) 100vw, 1248px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eLa Flèche is a residence defined by clarity, restraint, and warmth. MU Architecture has crafted a home that feels rooted in place while offering space to connect, rest, and reflect.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography by Raphael Thibodeau | Architects/designers: MU Architecture | Team: Charles Cote, Jean-Sebastien Herr, Magda Telenga, Pierre-Loup Pivoin, Maude Hebert, Karine Taillon, Celeste Main, Sakiko Watatani | Decoration: Les Ensembliers | Cabinetery: Atelier Jacob | Structural Engineer: GenieX | Mechanical and Civil Engineer: LH2 | Contractor: Groupe Laverdure Construction | Landscaping: Concept les Ensembliers \u0026amp; Work: Northland\u003c/h6\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
